# Ignore real OGG Vorbis music bytes. Placeholders are committed via
# git add -f so the //go:embed directive compiles on a fresh checkout.
# Drop real id1/music/track02..11.ogg from the Quake archive into this
# directory and rebuild to get music playback.
*.ogg
!track02.ogg
!track03.ogg
!track04.ogg
!track05.ogg
!track06.ogg
!track07.ogg
!track08.ogg
!track09.ogg
!track10.ogg
!track11.ogg
